long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Experience the celestial beauty and immense power of Kaguya with this Chrome extension, featuring mesmerizing live wallpapers that showcase her divine form. From the hit anime Naruto, Kaguya's otherworldly presence is now brought to life on your browser with stunning visuals.

Features:
🎨 High-quality live wallpapers of Kaguya in her divine form.
🌐 Customizable search bar supporting your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display for a personalized touch.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for fast navigation to your favorite sites.
Immerse yourself in the majestic and powerful presence of Kaguya every time you open a new tab, making this extension perfect for fans of Naruto and celestial-themed art.
